summary: The document is a forensic analysis report from ABC Forensic Services Laboratory, detailing the comparison of fired cartridge cases. It concludes that the cartridge case CW-8A and the test cartridge case BCSO-3.5 were fired by the same firearm. The Glock 17 pistol (BCSO-3) was not used in this examination.
conclusion: The cartridge case CW-8A and the test cartridge case BCSO-3.5 were determined to be fired by the same firearm based on microscopic comparison.
